reviewText: He doesnt play the tab that is written so make sure you purchase his DVD!
An excellent guitar instruction book in a series of such books.

This is a very finely executed educational DVD. I'm intermediate level on my playing skills, and this DVD provides licks that are simple enough to learn quickly but not so simple that they are insulting to my abilities.
I would highly recommend this DVD to anyone that wants to learn new licks and applying them into their playing.
